name: CC_cal_temp
notes: cal_temp = FACTORY Calibration water temperature value

name: CC_di
notes: di = (1 x 256) array of deionized water reference spectrum (in-house calibration 2016_05_12)

name: CC_eno3
notes: eno3 = (1 x 256) array of wavelength-dependent nitrate extinction coefficients

name: CC_eswa
notes: eswa = (1 x 256) array of seawater extinction coefficients

name: CC_lower_wavelength_limit_for_spectra_fit
notes: Constant.  wllower = Lower wavelength limit for spectra fit.(4-cm pathlength probe tip)

name: CC_upper_wavelength_limit_for_spectra_fit
notes: Constant.  wlupper = Upper wavelength limit for spectra fit.

name: CC_wl
notes: wl = (1 x 256) array of wavelength bins
